---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
    <main class="p-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-[#2b361c]">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#636b3f] mb-4">Collaborators</h1>

        <p class="text-[#2b361c] mb-4">
            The AURA Protocol is an open and collaborative effort driven by experts in artificial intelligence, scientific reproducibility, and digital ethics. It brings together researchers, developers, and educators committed to promoting transparency and accountability in the use of generative AI.
        </p>

        <div class="mb-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#b17036] mb-2">Lead Contributor:</h2>
            <p class="text-[#2b361c]">
                <strong>Dr. Fausto David Cortés Rojas</strong> – Researcher and professor in Biomedical Engineering, with specialization in AI transparency, image processing, and ethical applications of generative models. He has authored peer-reviewed publications and led interdisciplinary research projects at the intersection of technology and medicine.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-[#636b3f] mt-2 space-y-1 ml-4 list-disc list-inside">
                <li>
                    <a href="https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5224-5710" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline" target="_blank">ORCID Profile</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="https://www.webofscience.com/wos/author/record/MFI-2232-2025" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline" target="_blank">Web of Science Author Record</a>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#b17036] mb-2">Contributing Technologies:</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-[#2b361c] space-y-1 ml-4">
                <li>OpenAI API – GPT-based generation used during protocol drafting</li>
                <li>Astro Framework – Static site generation and publishing</li>
                <li>GitHub – Collaborative version control and public contributions</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-[#d4a369] italic">
            Interested in contributing to the protocol, suggesting improvements, or joining the initiative? Reach out via <a href="mailto:fdavid.cortezr@cinvestav.mx" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">email</a> or submit proposals on <a href="https://github.com/drfcortes/aura.org" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">GitHub</a>.
        </p>
    </main>
</Layout>
